<heading>drop - Drop an item from inventory.</heading>
<rule/>
<heading level="2">Usage</heading>
<pre>drop NAME</pre>
<heading level="2">Description</heading>
<paragraph>Removes a portable box from your inventory and places it at the current location.</paragraph>
<heading level="2">Examples</heading>
<pre>drop Key
  Drop the Key at the current location.</pre>
<heading level="2">See also</heading>
<paragraph>inv, look, move, place, take</paragraph>
